	<contents_en>Add the function of language syntax highlight settings.\nAdd the function of the brackets auto match, auto insert and deleting.\nAdd the function of auto match and auto completion of html/xml tags.\nAdd the function of displaying the indent indication.\nAdd the function of "Open with SimpleNotePad" command in the explorer context menu.\nAdd the function of File Relate.\nAdd the function of the default encoding format setting.\nAdd the function to insert date time.\nAdd the function of the monitoring mode.\nAdd the function to sync the settings to all open SimpleNotePad process.\nAdd the function of file reload.\nFixed the problem that the line number cannot be scaled with the document scale.\nFixed the problem that the result is sometimes incorrect after executing "Replace All".\nFixed the problem that the program may crash caused by failure to load the recent file list.\nFixed the problem that the find function cannot be continued even if the cursor position is changed after search complete when "Wrap around" is not checked.\nFixed the problem that the length of the text input in the text box in the Find Replace dialog could not exceed the text box width.\nFixed the problem that the selected text would not be replace after paste.\nThe default encode format for save is changed to the current encode format, instead of always ANSI.\nAdded the function of cover original files and add folder in the "Encoding Batch Conversion" dialog.\nAdded the support of UTF8 without BOM, UTF16BE, UTF16LE encoding format in the "Encoding Batch Conversion" dialog.\nChange the Ctrl+W shortcut to exit and the wrap shortcut to Ctrl+Shift+W.\nFixed the problem that the extra zero character would appear at the end of the file when save the document as UTF16 format.\nImprovements in other details.</contents_en>
